body: So yeah first part already translated but the rest. They all fail and in the end the janitor turns up and say's he always have to clean up after the students and get's her pregnant. Then the next one I believe is a husband wife where the husband had to go away for a while. But because of the law the wife has to be pregnant so the dad + brothers starts to sleep with her to make sure she get's pregnant. Last one is son takes home friends to sleep with the mom then mom opens the door to a bunch of women saying she also brought her friends.
